WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:02.000
I want you to get on your knees and apologize

2
00:00:02.066 --> 00:00:02.900
Luo Xueqi

3
00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:05.833
With me

4
00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:12.966
Miss, I have been a nanny in your hometown for 15 years

5
00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:15.266
I was afraid that you would take her

6
00:00:15.733 --> 00:00:16.400
Dad, what are you doing?

7
00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:18.400
Stop playing the emotional card for me here

8
00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:19.900
The fault of raising a godmother or not

9
