13
00:00:27.966 --> 00:00:29.800
What dignity can a nanny's daughter have?

14
00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:31.400
You beggar lowly people

15
00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:33.300
It's ridiculous, you all shut up for me

16
00:00:33.900 --> 00:00:36.033
Mom, let's go home

17
00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:37.600
Walk home

18
00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:39.633
Don't be so childish, okay?

19
00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:42.566
Either you kneel down for me today

20
00:00:42.566 --> 00:00:46.233
Either you two leave the arena

21
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:49.700
If I leave Jiangcheng

22
00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:52.466
