23
00:00:55.066 --> 00:00:56.766
We can leave Jiangcheng

24
00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:03.466
What are you doing?

25
00:01:03.466 --> 00:01:06.300
I'm going to Miss Dare, you don't want Mr. Wang

26
00:01:07.333 --> 00:01:08.300
Things between us

27
00:01:08.300 --> 00:01:09.966
Why are you bullying my mother?

28
00:01:10.100 --> 00:01:12.400
Lin Hong, have you thought about it?

29
00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:14.066
My world is precious

30
00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:18.366
Mom, don't believe what he says, he believes it.

31
00:01:19.733 --> 00:01:21.500
As long as you let go

32
